data.description: Welcome Home to Your Oasis on Just Under Two Acres! This charming property boasts all the comforts of home and more. With three spacious bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a double bonus room upstairs, there's plenty of room for everyone. The primary bedroom on the main level provides convenience and privacy, while the rest of the house offers ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Step outside onto the rocking chair front porch to greet the day with stunning sunrise views. In the evenings, unwind on the rear porch and take in breathtaking sunsets. If you've always dreamt of a self-sustaining lifestyle, you're in luck! This property is perfect for those who want to bring the chickens, with plenty of space for a coop. Inside, the cozy living room features a brick fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere during the colder months. Safety is a priority with a storm shelter located in the backyard, providing peace of mind during severe weather. For those who love to tinker or need extra storage, the large workshop/barn in the back is a dream come true. It comes equipped with electricity and a wood-burning stove, making it a versatile space for hobbies and projects. The yard is a gardener's paradise, adorned with pecan trees, fig bushes, a chestnut tree, and peach trees. You can enjoy fresh, homegrown produce right from your own land. Nature enthusiasts will appreciate the regular visits from deer, turkey, and rabbits in the yard, making this property a true haven for wildlife lovers. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this unique property your own. Schedule a showing today and make this welcoming home your own private retreat! Seller will offer concessions for paint and carpet.
